results.name: Abntu sequence (Bantu alphabetized): list the numbers which have no 2's in their decimal expansion, but sort the digits of each term into alphabetical order.
reference: M. J. Halm, Word Weirdness, Mpossibilities 66 (Feb. 1998), p. 5.
M. J. Halm, Sequences (Re)discovered, Mpossibilities 81 (Aug. 2002), p. 1.
formula: Digits are taken in the order 8 5 4 9 1 7 6 3 0.
xref: Cf. A057846 (supersequence), A225805 (French version of the latter).
